attachments.title: All-Star Portland chefs bake cookies for Planned Parenthood
attachments.text: A group of Portland's best-known women chefs are banding together to bake an epic cookie box ahead of Donald Trump's upcoming presidential inauguration, with proceeds going to the reproductive health nonprofit.
